dings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我已经完成了初始扫描分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"FailedPrecondition\", \"Can't access cart storage\", \"rpc error\", \"Redis\", \"cartstorage\", \"Kestrel\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice 无法访问 Redis 存储，导致 FailedPrecondition 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error status code 'FailedPrecondition' with detail 'Can't access cart storage.' raised. - 出现次数:171\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis 存储服务连接问题，cartservice 无法访问购物车存储\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Connecting to Redis: redis-cart:6379,ssl=false,allowAdmin=true,connectRetry=5 - 多次重连尝试\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\", \n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务在调用 cartservice 时遇到 RPC FailedPrecondition 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to add to cart: rpc error: code = FailedPrecondition desc = Can't access cart storage. - 出现次数:172\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**: 所有错误都围绕 `FailedPrecondition` 和 `Can't access cart storage`，表明购物车存储访问问题。\n\n2. **影响范围**: \n   - 涉及多个 frontend 实例 (frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2)\n   - 涉及多个 cartservice 实例 (cartservice-0, cartservice-1, cartservice-2)\n   - 跨多个节点 (aiops-k8s-01,04,05,07,08)\n\n3. **根因指向**: cartservice 无法连接到 redis-cart 存储服务，导致前端购物车功能失效。\n\n4. **故障严重性**: 错误日志出现频率很高（cartservice 错误171次，frontend 错误172次），表明这是一个影响范围较大的存储连接故障。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"pod_processes\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常指标包括 error_ratio 和 server_error_ratio 显著增加，表明服务端错误率上升。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio 从 0.0 上升到 0.63，server_error_ratio 从 0.0 上升到 0.63。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"re